HEADWORD: Blanchimeter
<hw>Blanch*im"e*ter</hw> <pr>(bl⟦adot⟧nch*⟦icr⟧m"⟦esl⟧*t⟦etil⟧r)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[1st <ets>blanch</ets> + <ets>-meter</ets>.]</ety>
